name: Bonnie Lawrence
text: I had heard about Papa Murphy's and finally gave it a try. The best pizza I have had in a very long time. The staff was amazing! If you have never been here you don't know what you're missing!

text: It's one of the only in the state of florida?? I'm from Minnesota and they are everywhere. Great pizza! Fresh and you bake it yourself. They don't delivery which stinks but can't get that quality pizza at many sit down spots

text: I love it.  You only get fresh, hot pizza straight out of the oven at a restaurant or at home.  I have enjoyed every one I have tried and I haven't had the same one twice.  Probably have had about seven different ones now.

text: I come here once or twice a week and always get the garden veggie pizza. It's a prepared style pizza that you have to take home and bake yourself. They are really fast (especially if you call ahead), and its hands down the best veggie pizza I've ever had!
